column5: Im going to go to caladonia on thursday in hopes of finding something crome lookin...have anyone been there lately?  much water or really low like most places?  thanks!

River is in great shape, very slight tea stain and the water level is just perfect. Find the holes and find the fish, was out this past saturday for a couple of hours and ended up with 1 nice chrome about 5-6 lbs.  Got to love the pull in the river, released for you on thursday, good luck.
Were you floating or on the fly?
